{"tid":2443174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"布林肯：譴責中國改變選舉制度扼殺香港民主","createTime":"2021-03-12T01:29:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T01:36:27.000Z","uid":350584,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ed2d0fcf1fa6803e049f32f9aa73a0688662e18b","tid":2443174,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:29:06.000Z","msg":"美國譴責中國改變香港的選舉制度，批評北京扼殺香港的民主。<br />\n<br />\n國務卿布林肯發表聲明說，中國全國人大會議的決定，是對《中英聯合聲明》承諾給予香港高度自治的直接打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580183-20210312.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580183-20210312.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=2a4f2691\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580183-20210312.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1e4f7910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580183-20210312.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a4581ed805f8c4f5b190dea46343bc32d67958d2","tid":2443174,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:29:22.000Z","msg":"布林肯指，中國通過限制政治參與，減少民意代表和扼殺政治討論，剝奪香港人的聲音。美國敦促中國和香港當局容許在9月如期進行立法會選舉，並確保透明，讓所有候選人都可以參選。<br />\n<br />\n布林肯又要求當局撤銷控告根據香港國安法被檢控的民主派人士。"},{"pid":"c645fa6f285318b547ed1fad882f9137d8dc538a","tid":2443174,"uid":65738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"all talk on9ly"},{"pid":"783e805219fe0eb9e48015b905cd3c8a2aa0b544","tid":2443174,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:30:49.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國批評人大修改香港選舉制度，是直接攻擊香港自治。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人普賴斯：「我們譴責中方持續侵犯香港民主制度，人大於3月11日通過的草案，是直接攻擊香港自治、自由及民主進程，削弱政治參與，減少民主代表及扼殺政治辯論，蔑視港人清晰的意願，及否定他們的聲音。」"},{"pid":"f6a186e22adb24d51107378f903d3536878dfa03","tid":2443174,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:30:54.000Z","msg":"吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係改呀，咁點？"},{"pid":"82fbe7daba9cc6352ff8582986b34d8846d6542e","tid":2443174,"uid":266892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:30:59.000Z","msg":"譴責、批評、要求<br />\n你不如收皮啦"},{"pid":"58c37e3f59ad6eae2d359a0fd96675187215cc9d","tid":2443174,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:31:06.000Z","msg":"對於美國國務卿布林肯及國家安全顧問沙利文，稍後跟中共中央政治局委員，中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任楊潔篪，以及國務委員兼外長王毅面對面會談，普賴斯預期將會是棘手的對話，希望北京可以展現改善雙邊關係的意願。而白宮發言人普薩基指，美方屆時將毫無保留地，表達對台灣、香港以及在經濟關係方面的關注；亦會討論新疆的種族滅絕議題。"},{"pid":"7fb3988bf57f7b2e199b0b1952d2631a40a84cd4","tid":2443174,"uid":12599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NdqjFb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NdqjFb.gif&h=41cb5a52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"656e4dbb6a9f34fbdcf907654d26c163397d3942","tid":2443174,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:32:09.000Z","msg":"每一日譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019bbd50ae78b60df9894dacfda789b208c46b13","tid":2443174,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:32:24.000Z","msg":"由弊燈上台起  美共國務院已經同中共口交部無異"},{"pid":"fe95179a0353ce93c44422d950d192cdd54e8b06","tid":2443174,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGmSJ7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGmSJ7d.gif&h=f940790f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae2d90273f35b13d4daed35024d4ab66ad24c983","tid":2443174,"uid":227177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母聽都聽到悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d11cdcffcd853288896825dd39c4665dd70997","tid":2443174,"uid":143526,"l